OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Bill
OL,4,CGladdon
OL,6,FBill Gladdon, Aged 100, 6th Airborne
OL,7,FArmoured Recce Regiment
OL,9,FInterviewed 30 July 2023
OL,11,FDied 24 April 2024
OL,13,FWatching the men of the Ox and Bucks
OL,14,Ffly out from Tarrant Rushton on the
OL,15,Fnight of 5 June, Bill Gladdon followed
OL,16,Fon D-Day in a Hamilcar glider which
OL,17,Fwas also carrying Tetrarch light tanks.
