OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Bill
OL,4,CGladdon
OL,6,F"On the way over I couldn't see
OL,7,Fanything. I thought I would climb on
OL,8,Ftop of the tank. I saw other tow
OL,9,Fplanes and gliders in the air.
OL,11,F"Then the glider pilot dropped the tow
OL,12,Frope and you're not allowed to move
OL,13,Fbecause it upsets the weight for the
OL,14,Fglider pilot.
OL,16,F"So I had to freeze on top of this
OL,17,Ftank and that's how I landed in
OL,18,FNormandy, spreadeagled on top of a
OL,19,FTetrarch tank in a Hamilcar glider."
