OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Bill
OL,4,CGladdon
OL,6,F"I was pushed from one hospital to
OL,7,Fanother. I still haven't recovered. I
OL,8,Fstill get trouble."
OL,10,FMany years later Mr Gladdon learnt
OL,11,Fthat it was a Tiger Tank that had
OL,12,Ffired on him and his colleagues.
OL,14,FHe passed away eight months after this
OL,15,Finterview.
